title: PayPal Stock Rallies After Game-Changing Deal with OpenAI
description: PayPal (PYPL) shares surged 10.46% to $77.74 in premarket trading following a partnership with OpenAI to embed its digital wallet into ChatGPT, enabling seamless purchases for hundreds of millions of users starting next year. The deal positions PayPal as a key payments infrastructure for AI-driven commerce, handling backend processing, fraud…
